title: Bears-Packers, Mitchell Trubisky, Antonio Brown and Blazin' 5!

description:
Colin discusses Bears-Packers, Mitchel Tribiskey’s performance, what the Chicago Bears must be thinking, Raiders WR Antonio Brown not being suspended, and his Blazing 5 picks. Guests include Greg Jennings, Vic Tafur, Takeo Spikes, Brady Quinn, and Jason McIntyre.
